  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to AAlib</title>

    <para>
      <application>AAlib</application> is a library to render any graphic into
      ASCII Art.
    </para>

    &lfs130_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
      <listitem>
